AOC has revealed its new AGON AG352UCG curved LCD gaming monitor. The monitor features a 35-inch panel with a resolution of 3,440 x 1,440 and a maximum refresh rate of 100Hz. The display is a G-Sync monitor which includes AOC’s Flicker-Free and Low Blue Light reduction technologies. The monitor also includes red, green, or blue LED lighting, a built-in carry handle, and a retractable headset holder. The AG352UCG is priced at £799 and will be available from March 2017.